## CSS Separation Rules

**Vue `<style scoped>`** → Feature-specific layout & styles (`.pricing-parent`, `.hero-title`)

**`utilities.css`** → Reusable across features (`.card`, `.container`, `.grid`)

**Not use em, rem units** in CSS files.

**Not use max-width or max-height** in CSS files.

**Quick test:** Can it be used in multiple features? → `utilities.css`. Specific to one feature? → Vue component.

